cdata.name: SportyCo
cdata.desc: SportyCo is a decentralized sports investment & funding ecosystem. It aims tointroduce a brand new industry of sports crowd micro-financing, while providing athletes, clubs and sport organizations with macro-funding on their respective end.TheSPF token is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum network. Itwill be theprimary means of transactionson our platform. It will be used both for investing in athletes (and crowdsourcing donations) as well as other transactions on the platformwhich includes paid advertising, paid reach and other premium services offered. The SPF token will belisted on several exchangesto integrate it into the wider crypto ecosystem. Token holders will be able to participate in DAO voting steering the SportyCo Professional Funds operation.
